description:
ProSheets is a plugin for Autodesk Revit Add-in to batch export Views and Sheets to PDF, DWG, DGN, DWF, NWC, IFC, and Images (JPEG, PNG, TIFF, etc).


Bug Fixes
- The tool would crash for free users when the internet connection was unavailable.
- Missing IFC export option in Revit 2024 and newer: “Allow use of type properties in instance property sets”.
